TO SET UP A SLIP TRAP (GENERIC CATCHES ALL WITH S0C4)

SLIP SET,ID=TESi,COMP=0C4,A=SVCD,END



TO DELETE IT 

slip del,id=TESI


SLIP SET,COMP=0C4,JOBNAME=HLASMJOB,A=SVCD,END

ONLY FOR THAT JOB AND SOC4


SLIP SET,JOBNAME=HLASMJO,A=SVCD,END   (CATCHES ALL ABEND FOR THIS JOB)

SLIP SET,PVTMOD=(R),JOBNAME=MYJOB,A=SVCD,END

    PVTMOD=(R) → Watches private storage modifications.
    JOBNAME=MYJOB → Filters only for MYJOB.
    A=SVCD → Captures a dump for analysis.



